{
  "id": 2810,
  "name": "Muro'jin and Nekraxx",
  "description": "Muro'jin is a relentless tracker, charged with capturing victims for the Vilebranch's dark rites. Nekraxx, a reanimated eagle, strikes down any who resist capture by her master. They must not be allowed to supply souls for Vordaza's necrotic magic any longer.",
  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "Overview",
      "body_text": "The cunning duo of Muro'jin and Nekraxx fight as one, assailing players with an array of combined tactics.\r\n\r\nMuro'jin withers players down with [Barrage] while Nekraxx flings a salvo of feathers with [Fetid Quillstorm].\r\n\r\nAs Muro'jin scatters [Freezing Traps] across the arena, Nekraxx barrels forward with [Carrion Swoop].",
      "spell": null,
      "sections": [
        {
          "title": "Damage Dealers",
          "body_text": "$bullet;Muro'jin attempts to [Revive Pet] upon Nekraxx's defeat, and Nekraxx enters [Bestial Wrath] upon Muro'jin's defeat.\r\n$bullet;Muro'jin's [Freezing Traps] encase players in ice upon contact. Players encased in ice can intercept Nekraxx's [Carrion Swoop].\r\n$bullet;Muro'jin's [Barrage] follows the targeted player and affects all players in a frontal cone.",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Healers",
          "body_text": "$bullet;Nekraxx's [Infected Pinions] inflicts significant damage to all players.\r\n$bullet;Muro'jin's [Freezing Traps] encase players in ice upon contact. Players encased in ice can intercept Nekraxx's [Carrion Swoop].\r\n$bullet;Muro'jin's [Barrage] follows the targeted player and affects all players in a frontal cone.",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        },
        {
          "title": "Tank",
          "body_text": "$bullet;Muro'jin's [Flanking Spear] both repositions behind his current target and applies [Open Wound].\r\n$bullet;Muro'jin's [Freezing Traps] encase players in ice upon contact. Players encased in ice can intercept Nekraxx's [Carrion Swoop].\r\n$bullet;Nekraxx's [Carrion Swoop] affects all players in its path, inflicting damage and knocking them upwards.",
          "spell": null,
          "sections": null
        }
      ]
    },
